data.description: Feel right at home in this well maintained and spacious 1822 square foot ranch style home. You will enjoy the 4 bedroom 2.5 bath floorplan, as well as, the open concept kitchen and living room. Picture yourself entertaining under the large gazebo and back patio area, and don't forget the wonderful large fenced private yard. This beauty boasts a 2 car attached garage as well as a 2 car detached garage/shop and the private yard has a large shed for all your lawn care needs. If you have an RV or trailer the subdivision has a secure lot that is included with your HOA fees for your needs. Come see it and fall in love with all this property has to offer.
